</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Osaka" /><category term="Bridges" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Crossing Osaka's Yodo River, we can see two of Osaka's many bridges: the New Yodogawa bridge in green, and behind it the Nagara Bridge in white. 大阪の淀川を渡ると、大阪の数多くの橋のうち2つが見える。緑色の新淀川大橋と、その奥に白い長柄橋だ。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2042.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2042.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Snow at Tenryuji・天龍寺の雪</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260105/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Snow at Tenryuji・天龍寺の雪" /><published>2026-01-05T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-01-05T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tenryuji-snow</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260105/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
